Talented Nigerian vocalist, Ric Hassani comes through with yet another impressive visuals for “Number One“. In his words, “We made this video for you and you have taken it as yours. My Friend ‘Prodigeezy‘ and i sat and said there is already too much on TV, let us make a video where it is just me, my choir, and You. I wrote this song, but these words are yours. Take these words and set them as the bar for the kind of love you deserve, and take nothing less“. Watch and Enjoy the new visuals for ‘Number One’, performed by Ric Hassani   The post [Video] Ric Hassani – “Number One” appeared first on tooXclusive. Source: Too Xclusive